Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their shape and abilities are\Nbased on their Soul Reaper's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers gain power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by learning their names\Nand synergizing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are born with Soul Reapers\Nand die with Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Zanpakuto are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense some faint\Nspiritual pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Okay!\N– Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Can you handle\Nthis on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a sword beast,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,NARUNOSUKE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is weird!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean… he's a Zanpakuto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I'm a Zanpakuto too, but…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I like older men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't like wimpy-looking guys\Nwho are clearly younger than me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't care less about him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I prefer slightly chubby older guys\Nto string beans like him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sparks are flying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is weird.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I like gutsy, testosterone-driven,\Nmanly men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not weak and\Npathetic guys like him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but a sword beast\Nis a sword beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get rid of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't look at me like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's triggering\Nmy maternal instincts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are things on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My side is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dealt with him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rangiku…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NDid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing\Nout of the ordinary! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.79,0:05:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey… Hey…\NMatsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Captain…\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're slacking off again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I was going to\Neat the manju I had been saving,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides…don't hide manju!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyorinmaru, get me some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must think my Zanpakuto\Nis your housekeeper, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, we still aren't done
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,eliminating all of\Nthe sword beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where is Haineko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably loafing\Naround somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't belong to an organization\Nlike the Soul Reapers…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I an enemy you\Nshould be chasing down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you treat my wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not petty enough to attack\Nan injured opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides…\Nunlike the other sword beasts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're not aggressive at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just saying anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, whatever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He seems perfectly normal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a sword beast,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the name\Nyou all have given me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a regular Zanpakuto\Nwho has lost his master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My master was\Na cowardly Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I'm just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to survive,\NI needed to protect myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to become friends\Nwith the other sword beasts…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end,\NI ended up being hunted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm hiding like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your injuries are still pretty bad.\NYou should rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're different from the other\NZanpakuto and the Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do something\Nabout your situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem dangerous at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask the others to treat you\Nlike a regular Zanpakuto
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of a sword beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.62,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,DON'T EAT!\NRANGIKU'S
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Narunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Haineko, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!\NYou make me sound old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Big Sister Haineko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me\Nsound even older!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when Zanpakuto\Nwho've lost their owners
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will go out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to deal with all\Nof them in the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there may be sword beasts\Nwho aren't dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish that were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we know from\NSquad 12's research
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that while each\Nsword beast is different,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a high possibility\Nthat they will eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lose their minds and\Ngo out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is to stop them before\Nsomething terrible happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you asking me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find a new sword beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just curious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Soul Reaper would dispose\Nof even a kid like him…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't mention him to them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she mentioned\Nthat sword beasts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}have a high possibility\Nof losing their minds…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does that mean there are\Nsword beasts who haven't?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right! He's different!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He said he was{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a regular Zanpakuto\Nwho had lost his master.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I explain things to Rangiku, \NI'm sure she'll understand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You like younger guys?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way. Gross.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I've got to do\Nsomething about it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Very!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't imagine a kid like him\Ngoing out of control.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's definitely not a sword beast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a regular Zanpakuto!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to eat with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, am I still going to\Nbe treated as a sword beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you talk to\Nsomeone about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh! That!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked my Soul Reaper\Nabout that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she would talk\Nto her superiors about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they're kind of\Nbusy right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it might take some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway,\Nabout my Soul Reaper…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an odd woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a bad person, but she\Ndid something funny recently…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't\Nhealed up completely…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miss Haineko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with you, I feel relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's\Nwonderful to be alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you, dear Rangiku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dear Rangiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're becoming\Nmore frequent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought lunch again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a little sake too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can drink, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wounds should be better now,\Nso have a drink with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Haineko …
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I still can't have\Nfun like you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.06,0:13:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I going to be dealt with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that\Nyou would handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No… Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword beast is\Njust a sword beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My situation has not changed,\Nbut it cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay here, Soul Reapers\Nwill come after me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to escape\Nbefore that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!\NNot in the state you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wounds have healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you. I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But we know from\NSquad 12's research{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that while each\Nsword beast is different, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there is a high possibility\Nthat they will{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}eventually lose their minds\Nand go out of control.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get headaches sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my hands start to\Ndo things on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, I've been worrying that\Nthey've become more frequent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you need to stay here until you\Nno longer have those headaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our supplies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been missing\Na lot of things lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is taking medicine\Nand food from the barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who it might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there may be sword beasts\Nwho aren't dangerous!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hanging around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you know\Nthat someone's been
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stealing medicine and food\Nfrom our barracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Honestly, it's disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?\NAt this rate…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay.\NYou just need some rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!\NWhat's going to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?\NHang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're becoming a sword beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all makes sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You followed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me\Nabout this earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you hide this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try to understand\Nmy position here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're my Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from that sword beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! He's not a sword beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll go beyond suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll lose his mind\Nand go out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens\Nto sword beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become\Na sword beast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There has to be\Na way to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Haineko…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save me…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way, Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting rid of him\Nfor his own good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then consider me a sword beast\Nand get rid of me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I can't reason with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Growl…\N– Growl…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no choice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to restrain\NHaineko with bakudo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Narunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haineko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Growl…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't\Nkeep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Haineko…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narunosuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miss Haineko…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Narunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.41,0:21:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making fun of me,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're foolish, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I still like younger guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I grow old,\Nit's never too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Captain, should we\Ngive something to Haineko
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to help her soothe\Nher broken heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.78,0:23:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Perhaps…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alcohol and shopping is always\Ngood for a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm worried about\NHaineko going off on her own,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all for Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.61,0:23:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Ishida, I want you\Nto make some cool clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.91,0:23:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that'll make Lieutenant Sasakibe\Nreally stand out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That cape…\NThat was popular in England!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.67,0:23:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you\Nshould go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Wow…\N– Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:24:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Sasakibe!\NThat really looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I incorporated a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.63,0:24:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,19th century English designs\Ninto it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.44,0:24:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:05.16,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.16,0:24:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,